where 
\begin_inset Formula $f,g\in C^{1,2}(\mathcal{I}\times\mathbb{R}^{d},\mathbb{R}^{d})$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $c^{(i)}=A^{(i)}e$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $e=(1,1,1,1)^{T}$
\end_inset

.
 The reduced constraints for additive noise were derived for order 1:
\end_layout

